# Semantic Keyword Palette (SKP)

When styling or naming anything tied to **bed**, **sleep/asleep**, **wake**, **alarm**, **nap**, etc., follow the **Semantic Keyword Palette (SKP)** documented in [docs/semantic-keyword-palette.md](docs/semantic-keyword-palette.md).

Use the CSS variables listed there (`--color-bed`, `--color-sleep`, `--color-up`, …) defined in `styles.css` instead of ad-hoc hex for those meanings. For new charts, timelines, or legends, match the same tokens the daily view uses.
